Package org.jogger.http.servlet.multipart

Interface Summary
PartHandler Implementations of this interface are passed to the Multipart.parse(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, PartHandler) method and handle the request parts.
 

Class Summary
Multipart Provides methods to check and parse multipart requests.
MultipartReader Low level API for processing file uploads.
ParameterParser A simple parser intended to parse sequences of name/value pairs.
Streams Utility class for working with streams.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidFileNameException This exception is thrown in case of an invalid file name.
MultipartException  
MultipartReader.IllegalBoundaryException Thrown upon attempt of setting an invalid boundary token.
MultipartReader.MalformedStreamException Thrown to indicate that the input stream fails to follow the required syntax.
